Package ohos.hiviewdfx

Class FaultLogger.FaultLogQueryResult

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.hiviewdfx.FaultLogger.FaultLogQueryResult
  • Enclosing class:
    FaultLogger

    public static final class FaultLogger.FaultLogQueryResult
extends Object
    Represents the query result of application fault records.

    You must destroy the query result when you are done using it.

    Since:
    5

      • destroy

        public void destroy​()
        Destroys the query result.

        After all fault records are obtained, you must call this method to release the resources of the current process and the server because only one active query result is allowed for each application at a time.

        Since:
        5
